de.sfgmbh.comlayer.core.controller

Class ViewManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.sfgmbh.comlayer.core.controller.ViewManager

  • public class ViewManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Manage instances of view objects as a lot of view objects shall be present only one time or need special treatment. This is helpful to avoid too complex dependency injection chains or a lot of singletons.
    Author:
    anna, hannes, denis
